{
  "stem": "10699.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Why didn't you run away?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Why didn't you run away?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The next day, they took us out, up again to the Gestapo, the, the Gestapo chief.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that guy kept asking questions again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They asked me, how many of you are you?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I said, we are three.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because he had arrested three of us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Although the Gestapo saw-- could see that I wasn't telling the whole truth because they had the six cards, he didn't say anything.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the Milice was listening to the conversation outside.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he came in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he said, she's lying.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We arrested her brother.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] What they had done--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had gone to the hospital.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my brother was coming out of an eye operation, bandaged completely, in between two nuns.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they come in-- and as-- you know, the Milice comes in civilian clothes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They said, have you got David Silberberg?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They said, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's him.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] So they took him, all with his eyes bandaged, to the prison-- to the-- [CRYING] to [FRENCH].",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The next-- The thing was that these nuns-- when we came back he needed another operation, tonsil operation-- they said, we prayed all year for you because we didn't realize that was the Gestapo-- that was the, the Milice.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Milice were the--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Vichy government had formed a new-- a, a new kind of army, which was the Milice, which was a kind of SS, you know, it was a German SS.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They worked for the German government under Vichy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] The next day my father who was out looking for food, he came back.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were waiting for him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So, you see, they got one after the other.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they, they-- and eventually took us.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
